content.p: Natasha completed both her Foundation in Science and her Degree in Environmental Science at University of Nottingham Malaysia (UNM). After acquiring a BSc in Environmental Science, she was part of the Malayan Tiger Conservation scene for 2 years. She is currently pursuing postgraduate research at UNM beginning in 2021.
